02 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 28: 2-4. </div><div class="t m1bd x63 he y363 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m1fc1 x3f he y3a0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What part have the angels in the work of salva- </div><div class="t m1cfb x64 he y8b8 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tion? Heb. 1: 13, 14. Note 1. </div><div class="t m286 x63 he y7b1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m12d4 x3f he ya76 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How is the good news of even one soul converted </div><div class="t m1635 x29 he yb9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">received among the angels? Luke 15: 10. </div><div class="t m1f3 x63 he y544 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t m660 x3f he y470 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What help in trial is assured to all who fear God? </div><div class="t m2b85 x64 he y725 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ps. 34:7. </div><div class="t m41c xc5 he yaf0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10. </div><div class="t m28d1 x3f he yaef ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What influence should their presence and minis- </div><div class="t m1727 x64 he y1641 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tration have upon our conduct? Matt. 18: 10; 1 Tim. </div><div class="t m2bb2 x29 he y76f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5:21. Note 2. </div><div class="t m41c xc5 he y5a1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">11. </div><div class="t mc62 x3f he y8c1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What is said of angel witnesses to our words? </div><div class="t m10f3 x64 he y786 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Eccl. 5: 6. </div><div class="t m41c xc5 he y549 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12. </div><div class="t m1a02 x3f he y66c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What part will the holy angels take in the events </div><div class="t m21b2 x29 he y122a ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Christ&apos;s second coming? Matt. 25: 31; 16: 27; 2 </div><div class="t mc5f x29 he ycc4 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Thess. 1: 7, 8. </div><div class="t m41c xc5 he y3ad ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. </div><div class="t mf39 x12 he y90e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What will they then do for the heirs of salvation </div><div class="t mbf x29 he ycf8 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for whom they have ministered? Matt. 24: 31. </div><div class="t m1708 x9a h21 y54d ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Notes </div><div class="t m1296 x66 he y1258 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. &quot;As those who have an understanding of Bible truth </div><div class="t m95 x29 he y3e2 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">try to seek out the men and women who are longing for light, </div><div class="t m527 x29 he y8c6 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">angels of God will attend them. And where angels go, none </div><div class="t ma8b x29 he y5e7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">need fear to move forward. As a result of the faithful efforts </div><div class="t m595 x29 he y344 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of consecrated workers, many will be turned from idolatry to </div><div class="t m2ec x29 he y6db ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the worship of the living God. Many will cease to pay hom-</div><div class="t md19 x29 he y4f5 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">age to man-made institutions, and will take their stand fear- </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
